                PartStory(
                    "“Maybe I am a lion” thought the little mouse. So he ran over to where all the lions lived, in a great big cage surrounded by great big bars to stop the lions escaping.  Being so small, the little mouse scampered straight through the bars to meet the great big lions inside. Taking a great big breath (which isn’t actually very big if you’re a little mouse), he let out the biggest ROAR he could. But because he was such a little mouse, all that came out was a tiny squeak. All the lions fell about laughing.",
