                PartStory(
                    "“In that case”, the little muse thought, “I MUST be an eagle”. So he ran over to where all the ginormous eagles lived, in a ginormous cage covered with a ginormous net to stop the eagles escaping.  Being so small, the little mouse easily slipped straight through the netting to meet the ginormous eagles inside. Trying to fly, he jumped in the air and flapped his little mouse legs as fast as he could. But try as he might, he just kept falling over on his bottom. All the eagles fell about laughing.",
